name: Uncharted Settlements
Text: 'Deploy on [Virtual Block 4] Hidden Base.  Organized Attack, S-foils, Revolution, Your Destiny (unless you chose Rebel/Rebel Starship), and [Virtual Block 4] Ellorrs Madak are canceled.  You may not deploy operatives or [Maintenance] cards.  Force generation at Endor system may not be canceled.  Unless Leave Them To Me on table, opponent''s combat vehicles, Dark Jedi, [Maintenance] cards, and [Permanent Weapon] cards are deploy +2 to Rebel Cell sites.  Opponent generates no Force at Hidden Landing Site. (Immune to Alter.)',
